Confirmed FMD outbreaks of 3 and 4 Jun 2010
--------------------------------------------
1. FMD situation as of 03 Jun 2010
----------------------------------
On Thu 03 Jun 2010, 5 new outbreaks (Nos 265 - 269) were confirmed as
PCR positive, as follows:

Number /District/Municipality/Animal sort/ Sampling date/ comment
-----------------------------------------------------------------
265. Koyu/ Shintomicho/ Beef cattle/ 02 Jun/ Vaccinated 25 May
266. Koyu/ Takanabe Town/ Beef cattle/ 02 Jun/Vaccinated 25 May
267. Koyu/ Kawaminami Town/ Beef cattle/ 03 Jun/Vaccinated 25 May
268. Koyu/ Kawaminami Town/ Swine / 03 Jun / Vaccinated 24 May
269. Koyu/ Tsuno Town/ Beef cattle / 03 Jun / Vaccinated 26 May

2. FMD situation as of 04 June 2010
-----------------------------------
On Fri 04 Jun 2010, 2 new outbreaks (Numbers 270 - 271) were
confirmed as PCR positive, as follows:

Number /District/Municipality/Animal sort/ Sampling date/ comment
-----------------------------------------------------------------
270. Koyu/ Kawaminami Town/ Swine/ 02 June/ Vaccinated 24 May
271. Koyu/ Shinomicho / Beef cattle / 04 June / Vaccinated 29 May

