Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[Reportedly, the above cases showed FMD signs. The appearance of
clinical signs within a week of vaccination is not surprising;
animals may have been incubating when vaccinated, or infected before
immunity established. Hopefully, such cases will disappear during the
coming week, while the culling, preferably performed under strict
biosecurity conditions, advances. - Mod.AS]

